value.name: Jimi ni Sugoi! Kôetsu Girl Kôno Etsuko... ga Inai Suiyôbi
value.original_name: 地味にスゴイ！校閲ガール・河野悦子…がいない水曜日
value.overview: Yoneoka and Fujiiwa work on the proofreading of a novel in the quiet proofreading department office when Etsuko is on annual leave and the novel's content becomes real-life footage in their minds.
